    "For integer entries with non-zero units digits, we shift the decimal point one place to the left, apply the method to the transformed values, and then shift them back.",
    "To prevent significant distortion, we exclude entries with absolute values less than 1 from watermarking.",
    "GLW is applied to all numerical columns across all datasets.TabularMark.",
    "Following the original experimental setup, we select the first numerical column as the watermark attribute, from which 10% of the cells are pseudorandomly chosen as key cells.",
    "The perturbation range p is set to 25, and the number of unit domains k to 500."
